{
  "id": "6227bc837a9bdc001d6612d9",
  "title": "更新行をスクロールバーに表示",
  "created": 1646771335,
  "updated": 1673226193,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6227bc837a9bdc001d6612d9",
      "text": "更新行をスクロールバーに表示",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646771335,
      "updated": 1646806027
    },
    {
      "id": "6227bc878ee92a0000549e3d",
      "text": " 標準機能になったみたい 2022/3/9 [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646771335,
      "updated": 1646771346
    },
    {
      "id": "6227bc878ee92a0000549e3e",
      "text": " このせいで[視線]が右に移動することが多くなったかも",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646771335,
      "updated": 1646771377
    },
    {
      "id": "6227bc968ee92a0000549e3f",
      "text": " 全行未読だと何も表示されないようだ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646771350,
      "updated": 1646783351
    },
    {
      "id": "622842918ee92a0000316889",
      "text": "  そういう仕様らしいです [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646805650,
      "updated": 1646805658
    },
    {
      "id": "6228429f8ee92a000031688a",
      "text": "  私は普通に表示すればいいと思うのですが、なんかウザいらしい [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646805664,
      "updated": 1646805681
    },
    {
      "id": "62288e791280f0000014f3ee",
      "text": "   まあわからんでもないかも[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646825080,
      "updated": 1646825084
    },
    {
      "id": "62288e7d1280f0000014f3ef",
      "text": "   でもそれならDOM作って`display: none`するだけでいいような",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646825084,
      "updated": 1646825103
    },
    {
      "id": "62288e901280f0000014f3f0",
      "text": "    これなら表示したい人だけ表示できる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646825103,
      "updated": 1646825127
    },
    {
      "id": "6229196c8ee92a0000c4b8c6",
      "text": "   未読のとき表示するかどうかで [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646860652,
      "updated": 1646860669
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d168ee92a000002640f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820631,
      "updated": 1646820631
    },
    {
      "id": "62287ce78ee92a0000026404",
      "text": "以下のUserScriptを入れると未読でも表示されるようになります [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820583,
      "updated": 1646820602
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a0000026407",
      "text": "code:script.js",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a0000026408",
      "text": " const dummyUnread = document.createElement('div')",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a0000026409",
      "text": " dummyUnread.classList.add('unread')",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a000002640a",
      "text": " const dummy = document.createElement('div')",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a000002640b",
      "text": " dummy.classList.add('telomere')",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a000002640c",
      "text": " dummy.appendChild(dummyUnread)",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "62287d0e8ee92a000002640d",
      "text": " document.body.appendChild(dummy)",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646820622,
      "updated": 1646820622
    },
    {
      "id": "6227eb571280f00000c44d43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646783319,
      "updated": 1646783319
    },
    {
      "id": "6227f1321280f000004c73fb",
      "text": " 挙動に不満がある[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646784817,
      "updated": 1646784833
    },
    {
      "id": "6227f13f1280f000004c73fd",
      "text": "   テロメアとスクロールバーのツマミの位置にズレがある",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646784830,
      "updated": 1646805955
    },
    {
      "id": "622843e01280f00000c4038f",
      "text": "    smartphoneで特に気になった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646805982,
      "updated": 1646806018
    },
    {
      "id": "622844171280f00000c40390",
      "text": "    と感じたのだが直っているかも",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646806038,
      "updated": 1646806048
    },
    {
      "id": "622867231280f00000dab1bd",
      "text": "    いややっぱりずれてる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646815010,
      "updated": 1646815019
    },
    {
      "id": "622937c61280f00000899ae9",
      "text": "    [/mw-internet/2022.03.10#6228a62b13a1580000147fb8]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646868421,
      "updated": 1646868421
    },
    {
      "id": "622937c61280f00000899aea",
      "text": "     たぶん同じことに言及している",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646868422,
      "updated": 1646868428
    },
    {
      "id": "622843cd1280f00000c4038e",
      "text": "   クリックで該当箇所にジャンプしたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646805964,
      "updated": 1646805980
    },
    {
      "id": "6228a45fe5172d0000fa11c3",
      "text": "    これが無いのつらい[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1646830688,
      "updated": 1646830703
    },
    {
      "id": "624294a2e5172d0000369c38",
      "text": "    スクロールバー上でジャンプできるショートカットを使う手がある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1648530593,
      "updated": 1648530723
    },
    {
      "id": "62429524e5172d0000369c3a",
      "text": "     [/NotaAllStarsMeetup/Nota ALL STARS  Meetup vol.3 ディスカッション・質疑応答#6241a44e97c2910000d8b319]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1648530723,
      "updated": 1648530724
    },
    {
      "id": "62429473e5172d0000369c37",
      "text": "     [/icons/Windows.icon][/icons/GoogleChrome.icon]：Shift+クリック",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1648530546,
      "updated": 1648530623
    },
    {
      "id": "624294c1e5172d0000369c39",
      "text": "     [/icons/macOS.icon][/icons/GoogleChrome.icon]：Alt+クリック",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1648530625,
      "updated": 1648530703
    },
    {
      "id": "6243a32b1280f00000fff80b",
      "text": "     [/icons/firefox.icon]：なさそう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1648599852,
      "updated": 1648599885
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb66101280f00000ce3428",
      "text": "    2023-01-09簡単なコードで作れた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225744,
      "updated": 1673225801
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb66191280f00000ce3429",
      "text": "     これ書いた後[/NotaAllStarsMeetup/Nota ALL STARS  Meetup vol.3 ディスカッション・質疑応答#6241a44e97c2910000d8b319]に行ったら、全っっっく同じコードが置いてあったOTL",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225753,
      "updated": 1673225816
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb66581280f00000ce342a",
      "text": "      一応、真ん中にスクロール位置を合せるか否で違いはあるけど……",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225816,
      "updated": 1673225843
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb66731280f00000ce342b",
      "text": "     今使った15分間は何だったの……？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225843,
      "updated": 1673225925
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb66a31280f00000ce342c",
      "text": "      問題演習を2週したと思うことにしよう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225891,
      "updated": 1673225915
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb674c1280f00000ce342d",
      "text": "     10:01:02 `scrapbox.Layout !== \"page\"`なページに遷移すると`.scroll-bar-overlay`が消えてしまう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226060,
      "updated": 1673226089
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb676d1280f00000ce342e",
      "text": "      対策として、`layout:changed`でlistenerを入れ直す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226093,
      "updated": 1673226128
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb63b21280f000005e09a6",
      "text": "    code:js",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225138,
      "updated": 1673225139
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb67951280f00000ce342f",
      "text": "     const render = () => {",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226135,
      "updated": 1673226163
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb67b31280f00000ce3433",
      "text": "       document.getElementsByClassName(\"scroll-bar-overlay\")[0]?.addEventListener?.(\"click\", (e) => {",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226163,
      "updated": 1673226173
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb63ee1280f000005e09a9",
      "text": "         if (!(e.target instanceof HTMLDivElement)) return;",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225198,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb64091280f000005e09aa",
      "text": "         if (!e.target.classList.contains(\"unread-bar\")) return;",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225225,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb64231280f000005e09ab",
      "text": "         const ratio = parseFloat(e.target.style.top) * 0.01;",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225251,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb64581280f000005e09ac",
      "text": "         globalThis.scroll({",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225304,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb659a1280f000005e09ad",
      "text": "           top: document.body.scrollHeight * ratio - globalThis.innerHeight /2",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225626,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb659e1280f000005e09ae",
      "text": "         });",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225630,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb63d91280f000005e09a8",
      "text": "       }, { capture: true });",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225177,
      "updated": 1673226182
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb67c11280f00000ce3434",
      "text": "     };",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226177,
      "updated": 1673226179
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb67c71280f00000ce3435",
      "text": "     render();",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226183,
      "updated": 1673226185
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb67a21280f00000ce3431",
      "text": "     scrapbox.on(\"layout:changed\", render);",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673226146,
      "updated": 1673226193
    },
    {
      "id": "63bb66021280f00000ce3427",
      "text": "     ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1673225730,
      "updated": 1673225730
    },
    {
      "id": "6227f14a1280f000004c73fe",
      "text": "  ので作り直すつもり",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646784841,
      "updated": 1646784873
    },
    {
      "id": "622842d48ee92a000031688b",
      "text": "  どのへんが不満ですか? [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1646805717,
      "updated": 1646805723
    },
    {
      "id": "6227f1321280f000004c73fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1646784817,
      "updated": 1646784817
    },
    {
      "id": "63bad5d5e5172d0000b2892c",
      "text": "　スマホで、横に長い数式や表があるページはズームアウトできるが、[ページをズームアウトするとスクロールバーのテロメアの位置がずれる][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1673188822,
      "updated": 1673189005
    },
    {
      "id": "63bad5d5e5172d0000b2892d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1673188822,
      "updated": 1673188822
    },
    {
      "id": "63905445e5172d00008bc09a",
      "text": "[スクロールバーのテロメア]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1670403141,
      "updated": 1670403150
    },
    {
      "id": "6390544ae5172d00008bc09b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1670403146,
      "updated": 1670403146
    }
  ]
}